text: Jacqueline van Rozendaal-van Gerven (born 20 February 1964) is a Dutch archer. Rozendaal-van Gerven competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics.Jacqueline van Rozendaal-van GervenJacqueline VAN ROZENDAAL == References == Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch archers Category:Olympians for the Netherlands Category:Sportspeople from 's-Hertogenbosch
